ëíŸ@f3e91f8abeb5782766941218cdc2ce42524f4d5942132bd3a9e40be259f39606⁄˙Title: This week in Nu #40
Path: This week in Nu #40
Content:
JosephTLyons added more help for contributors to 
[link: http://contributing.md] CONTRIBUTING.md
 (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1865] #1865
), improve the 
``cal``
 implementation (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1886] #1885
) and documentation (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1895] #1895
), added ctrl-c support to 
``du``
 (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1901] #1901
)
AarconC81 added completions for binaries in the PATH (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1866] #1866
)
shiena fixed a link in our Japanese documentation (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/book/pull/101] #101
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/book/pull/103] #103
)
Kelli314 helped improved light mode table printing (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1871] #1871
)
q-b helped fix some typos in the book (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/book/pull/102] #102
)
k-brk added 
``--to-float``
 to the 
``str``
 command (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1872] #1872
), improved the 
``with-env``
 shorthand (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1900] #1900
)
jzaefferer documented the new 
``--save``
 flag for 
``alias``
 (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1874] #1874
)
thegedge simplified the logic in the 
``parse``
 command (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1875] #1875
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1904] #1904
)
EmNudge documented the 
``trim``
 command (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1876] #1876
)
notryanb fixed some flaky external command tests (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1878] #1878
)
andrasio converted the 
``split``
 commands into sub-commands (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1879] #1879
), moved 
``str``
 to being a built-in command (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1908] #1908
), fixed an issue with plugins not having "end_filter" called correctly (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1914] #1914
), updated docs for 
``split``
 and 
``from``
 (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/book/pull/104] #104
)
shaaraddalvi improved errors when sorting by invalid column (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1880] #1880
)
fdncred improved auto-pivot's configuration (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1888] #1888
), added "plugin_dir" to config docs (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1911] #1911
), got nu-jupyter working online (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_jupyter/pull/2] #2
)
jonathandturner optimized processing time for 
``where``
 and related commands (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1902] #1902
), made it-expansion work on lists (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1903] #1903
), allowed 
``echo``
 to iterate ranges (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1905] #1905
), simplified plugin directory scanning (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1910] #1910
)
